sentences.english: This is the French unique humanities landscape, full of poetic.
sentences.chinese: 这是法国独特的人文景观，充满诗情画意。

sentences.english: Chuxiong state has rich natural and human landscape.
sentences.chinese: 楚雄州有丰富的自然资源和人文景观。

sentences.english: Garden name and landscape name belong to important parts of humane landscape.

sentences.english: Longnan has unique natural and man-made landscape.

sentences.english: The Seven-star scenic spot is the typical representative of combination of natural and human landscapes in Guilin.

sentences.english: Remains of the many monuments, unique human landscape, tourist resources to be developed.
sentences.chinese: 古迹遗存众多，人文景观独特，旅游资源有待开发。

sentences.english: Kunming is the natural landscape and humanistic landscape.
sentences.chinese: 昆明还是自然景观和人文景观的荟萃之地。

sentences.english: Longquan Temple is one of the symbolic humane scenery spots of the tourist zone in Qianshan.
sentences.chinese: 龙泉寺是千山风景区的标志性人文景观之一。

sentences.english: Liangshan has a unique natural landscape and cultural landscape, many places of interest.
sentences.chinese: 梁山有独特的自然景观和人文景观，名胜古迹众多。
